text: Olle Martinsson (born 21 March 1944) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Gällivare Municipality
